query:
INSERT INTO public.ship_info (
                symbol,
                display_name,
                role,
                active
                )
                SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                  $1::character varying[],
                  $2::character varying[],
                  $3::ship_info_role[],
                  $4::boolean[]
                 )
                 on conflict (symbol) DO UPDATE SET 
                display_name = EXCLUDED.display_name,
                role = EXCLUDED.role,
                active = EXCLUDED.active
